# =============================================================================
# AOXCHAIN - Workspace & Multi-Crate Rust Project Template
# Full Coverage: Rust, Node.js, Docker, Web & Security
# =============================================================================

# --- Node.js & Web Dependencies (CRITICAL) ---
# npm, yarn and pnpm folders anywhere in the tree
**/node_modules/
**/.pnpm-store/
**/.yarn/cache/
**/.yarn/unplugged/
**/.yarn/build-state.yml
**/.yarn/install-state.gz
**/.pnp.*
# Build outputs for frontend (React, Vue, Next.js vb.)
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.next/
**/.svelte-kit/
**/.nuxt/
# npm logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# --- Rust Workspace & Compilation (Global Coverage) ---
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk
**/cargo-incremental/
**/*.exe
**/*.so
**/*.dylib
**/*.dll
**/*.wasm
**/*.rlib

# --- Environment & Sensitive Data (SECURITY) ---
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.pfx
**/*.crt
**/secrets/
**/config/local_config.toml
**/credentials.json
.local
**/.local
# Cloud provider configs
**/.aws/
**/.gcloud/

# --- Blockchain / Node Specifics (Data & DBs) ---
**/data/
**/db/
**/ledger/
**/chain-data/
**/snapshots/
**/*.log
**/logs/
**/keystore/
**/wallets/*.json
!**/wallets/example.json

# --- Testing, Benchmarking & CI ---
**/tarpaulin-report.html
**/coverage/
**/target/criterion/
**/.nyc_output/
**/.cache/

# --- Docker & Containerization ---
**/.docker/
**/*.tar
**/*.tar.gz

# --- Python (If used for scripts/tools) ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/

# --- IDEs & Editors (Clean Workspace) ---
**/.vscode/*
!**/.vscode/settings.json
!**/.vscode/tasks.json
!**/.vscode/launch.json
!**/.vscode/extensions.json
*.code-workspace
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/.helix/
**/.project
**/.settings/

# --- System Files ---
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
**/*.swp
**/*~
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak
